quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  97,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  97,1,Innaa anzalnaahu fee lailatil qadr
  97,2,Wa maa adraaka ma lailatul qadr
  97,3,Lailatul qadri khairum min alfee shahr
  97,4,Tanaz zalul malaa-ikatu war roohu feeha bi izni-rab bihim min kulli amr
  97,5,Salaamun hiya hattaa mat la'il fajr
